{
  "stem": "1938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went to another camp, Foehrenwald.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Same what Solomon.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe different.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Foehrenwald, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is also in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's close to Munich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while I was there, I got a letter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a book, who was alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I read that Avram Manheimer, a brother of my fiance, is alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he is in the Feldafing camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he came, and he said I should stay with his wife.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He already-- he was 20 years old in '50, when he went to Auschwitz and Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said I should wait there with his wife, and he will go to Paris to see his brother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he picked him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "While he picked him up, he was already very sick, because he ran away from a running train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they shoot after him in the ribs, and he was very sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German people told him-- he went in in a house, and very friendly, and he thought that's it, that he is safe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they went and they called the police, and the police took him to Mauthausen of [INAUDIBLE] kommander for punishment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had very bad working under the ground in [NON-ENGLISH], and was very bad in making airplanes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the bottom line is, when I came out, I found him very sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I happened to be--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "45 years his nurse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where his brother was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was not well, because from all this working a few years under the ground with no air, with no food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was wounded, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How can he be well enough?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he had to go to a sanatorium right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in the chest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in-- in Gauting.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
